Additional features
-------------------
* show separators between exemplar (level 2 with different occ)
* highlight error lines at the grid
* action to sort tags
* add labels to toolbar elements
* better load records via unAPI and save records
* show record diffs
* show how to best apply syntax highlighting without an editor
* show information about the current field
* find tags and subfields
* show information about PPN and number of fields and exemplars
* show error messages
* search and highlight specific fields by tag and subfield
